Two-database architecture
=========================

- ``projects.db`` (shared metadata) — managed by Alembic.
- Per-project ``graph.db`` — managed at runtime by
  ``GraphBase.metadata.create_all(engine)`` inside ``DatabaseManager``.

Usage
-----

Default (projects.db)::

    alembic upgrade head
    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "..."

Graph schema::

    alembic -x db=graph revision --autogenerate -m "..."
    alembic -x db=graph upgrade head

The URL in ``alembic.ini`` is a fallback; the real URL is built
dynamically in ``env.py`` with ``~`` expansion and directory creation.
